Package: scaledic
Type: Package
Title: Functions and data frame extension for scale based operations
Version: 0.4.0
Date: 2025-05-05
Authors@R:
  person("Juergen", "Wilbert", 
    email = "juergen.wilbert@uni-potsdam.de", 
    role = c("cre", "aut"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8392-2873")
  )
Description: This package was designed to implement (psychometric) scale information to items of a data frame. 
  These include values, labels, subscales, weights etc.. A couple of functions help to organize, extract, replace missing values, find typos etc.
